## Solution & Delivery Considerations

Including Chaos Engineering practices and tools bring value to the application by making it resilient to a range of events and failures, however, it does require additional time and cost in development as well as operations of the application. When including Chaos engineering practices and tools in the delivery and management of an application, following set of considerations should be kept in mind:

